title: Judge Dredd - The Daily Dredds v01 - 1981-1986 (2014) (Digital)
description:
Judge Dredd - The Daily Dredds v01 - 1981-1986 (2014) (Digital) (DR & Quinch-Empire)


The works that went into the creation of this collection of Judge Dredd strips from the Daily Star is testament to the popularity of Old Stoney Face himself - this volumes as it is would not have been possible without the help of several fans, and the strips themselves are clearly the best thing printed within the pages of the Daily Star;)
